description: I never heard about a high-school for machinery and transportation. However, my first visitor today graduated from exactly that school. After that he already worked one time in a warehouse and afterwards at a cash desk. Long working hours and bad salary. Nothing new to me as I have a good feeling already about the average-salaries in the most different kind of jobs here in the Czech Republic. And therefore it was no surprise for me to hear that he currently still lives with his parents who still have to support him. Everything sounded quite promising to me but still it took me some time to convince him to strip in-front of me. He had a nice body. Great ass and big balls. He was so shy when I started to touch him. But then he even went down on his knees.
title: Dirty Scout 24
